荣耀.title: Respect and Communication
荣耀.description: All members must treat each other with respect and communicate in a friendly manner. Toxic behavior is not tolerated.

荣耀.title: Activity Requirements
荣耀.description: Members must log in at least 3 times a week. Inactivity for more than 7 days without notice may lead to removal.
